snippet: Teddy Bridgewater threw five touchdown passes, and the former Auburn star Michael Dyer had a 46-yard touchdown run as No. 9 Louisville defeated visiting Ohio, 49-7.
abstract: Louisville defeats Ohio, 49-7 in college football action.
